<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Age, asexual reproduction, and fire effects are not well known, but plants do sprout after fire or other disturbance (Desert Workshop 2000). Fire return intervals may be increasing where stands are adjacent to stands of fire-promoting <i>Tamarix </i>(Brooks and Minnich 2006).</div>
